@startuml 16.6_filterCommentBlog
hide footbox
title Filter Comment Post

actor User
boundary CommentPostPage as View
control CommentPostRoute as Route
participant ":AuthMiddleware" as Middleware
control "CommentPostController" as Controller
participant ":CommentPostService" as Service
participant ":CommentPostModel" as Model
database Database as Database

User -> View : 1. Select filter options\n(keyword, status)
activate View

    View -> Route : 3. GET /api/v1/comment?keyword=&status=&page=&size=
    activate Route

    Route -> Middleware : 4. AuthenticateUser(req, res, next)
    activate Middleware
    Middleware --> Route : 5. Authentication success
    Middleware -> Controller : 6. Forward FilterCommentBlogRequest(params)
    deactivate Middleware
    activate Controller

    Controller -> Service : 7. Process comment filtering
    activate Service

    Service -> Model : 7.1. Build filter criteria
    activate Model

    Model -> Database : 7.1.1. Retrieve filtered comment data
    activate Database
    Database --> Model : 7.1.2. Result set
    deactivate Database

    Model --> Service : 7.1.3. Return filtered list + paging info
    deactivate Model

alt No comments match
    Service --> Controller : 7.2. Return empty result
    Controller --> Route : 7.3. Return 200 OK + empty list/message
    Route --> View : 7.4. Show "No comments found" + keep filters
else Comments match
    Service --> Controller : 7.2. Return FilterCommentBlogResponse
    deactivate Service
    Controller --> Route : 7.3. Return 200 OK + filtered comments data
    deactivate Controller
    Route --> View : 7.4. Render filtered list + pagination
    deactivate Route
end

View --> User : 8. Display filter result
deactivate View
@enduml
